  "text": "Amazfit Active 2 $95 $130 Save $35 A sleek smartwatch that packs a ton of great features. Not only does it look good, but you also get excellent health and fitness tracking as well. Best of all, it's now just $95 for a limited time. A smartwatch allows you to stay in the moment, but also stay connected when it matters most. It's a subtle tool that can handle a variety of different parts of your life without interrupting it. And while there are plenty of great options if you're willing to spend $300 or more, the choices basically become non-existent once you're looking for something reliable at under $100. Related Best smartwatches for Android in 2025 Our favorite smartwatches for any Android phones That's where the Amazfit Active 2 comes in, with its super-sleek design, impressive features and incredible price that sits at just $95 right now. This is the lowest price we've seen for this smartwatch, which means if you've been thinking about picking up a new smartwatch, but wanted one at an affordable price, now's going to be the time. What's great about the Amazfit Active 2? Source: Amazfit The Amazfit Active 2 delivers a sleek and stylish design that's also quite versatile, making it the perfect wearable whether you're going to the gym or dressing up for a formal event. The case is made from stainless steel, and you also get a large 1.32-inch AMOLED display that delivers colors that pop and are still able to be seen, even in the brightest conditions. You also get an array of different sensors that can track your health and fitness metrics, along with sleep quality and cycle tracking. There are also activities built in, along with the Zepp Coach that can help you reach your fitness goals. If that wasn't enough, you also get excellent battery life, with the Active 2 lasting up to ten days on a single charge. You also get GPS tracking and downloadable maps too. Customization of the watch is also possible, with up to 400 different watch faces, and you can easily stay connected with notifications and alerts that come straight to your wrist. You can also respond to these messages using voice controls. Overall, not a bad watch for the price, and you won't have to pay for any extras to unlock the software features of the accompanying app. It all comes with this watch at this price, which is now just $95 from Amazon while this deal is still live. It's the best price we've seen on the Amazfit Active 2. Just make sure an Amazon Prime member to take advantage, otherwise it'll cost you $100, which is still a good deal.",
