\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/copy-of-169-21.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=500\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"2160\" height=\"1215\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Amazfit Active 2  on wrist\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/copy-of-169-21.png\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/copy-of-169-21.png\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                                    \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eSource: Amazfit\u003c/p\u003e\n                        \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Amazfit Active 2 delivers a sleek and stylish design that\u0026#39;s also quite versatile, making it the perfect wearable whether you\u0026#39;re going to the gym or dressing up for a formal event. The case is made from stainless steel, and you also get a large 1.32-inch AMOLED display that delivers colors that pop and are still able to be seen, even in the brightest conditions.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eYou also get an array of different sensors that can track your health and fitness metrics, along with sleep quality and cycle tracking. There are also activities built in, along with the Zepp Coach that can help you reach your fitness goals. If that wasn\u0026#39;t enough, you also get excellent battery life, with the Active 2 lasting up to ten days on a single charge.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eYou also get GPS tracking and downloadable maps too. Customization of the watch is also possible, with up to 400 different watch faces, and you can easily stay connected with notifications and alerts that come straight to your wrist. You can also respond to these messages using voice controls.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eOverall, not a bad watch for the price, and you won\u0026#39;t have to pay for any extras to unlock the software features of the accompanying app. It all comes with this watch at this price, which is now just $95 from Amazon while this deal is still live. It\u0026#39;s the best price we\u0026#39;ve seen on the Amazfit Active 2. Just make sure an Amazon Prime member to take advantage, otherwise it\u0026#39;ll cost you $100, which is still a good deal.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n            \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
